CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 30, 1957, pg. A9, reads: "Ivy League Time - It's spring and the Youth Lyceum Club of the Centre Avenue YMCA is sponsoring its third annual Youth Conference Program. Members of the registration and reception committee, left to right, are Jesse Peters, Merva Hardy, Donald Harris, Janice Harvey and Toni Bray. They are asking you to register by calling the YMCA MA. 1-1762. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Janice Harvey and Toni Bray seated, with Jessy or Jesse Peters, Merva Hardy, and Donald Harris standing in front of "Centre Avenue YMCA Youth Conference" banner
